__ Cantrip: Firestorm _________________________ Cost: 10 _____________________

Use:  cantrip firestorm                         Material Component: object
Use:  C firestorm

The cantrip firestorm is a minor magic of the sphere of evocation.  This 
rather spectacular cantrip calls down fire from the heavens to destroy
an object held in the hand of the caster.  Once destroyed, the object is
forever gone.
